I heard the "buy me some peanuts
and crackerjack." I

00:24:20.640 --> 00:24:22.030
heard that one.

00:24:22.030 --> 00:24:24.110
How about this one,
the Beatles?

00:24:24.110 --> 00:24:26.090
[SINGING]

00:24:26.090 --> 00:24:26.600
The answer--

00:24:26.600 --> 00:24:30.090
[SINGING]

00:24:30.090 --> 00:24:31.200
Big, Google.

00:24:31.200 --> 00:24:35.350
[SINGING]

00:24:35.350 --> 00:24:36.640
Nice and big!

