get around it and wrap

00:47:16.750 --> 00:47:18.770
ourselves around it and
make our effort to

00:47:18.770 --> 00:47:21.250
adjust to that key--

00:47:21.250 --> 00:47:24.030
in the long run, that can be the
idea that explodes, that

00:47:24.030 --> 00:47:25.850
is the next big idea.

00:47:25.850 --> 00:47:28.500
So this is the only way we get
